cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with knowledge base completion using graph neural networks, which is a popular topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves working with databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL) to some extent. Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests a possible connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
